_:Nd9f0cba5e7e94e979b7c6b4a84b995d8 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Shrinivas Honap is a Chartered accountant by profession and served with Vodafone, Capita, KPMG and Egg during his executive career.</p>\n\n<p>Shrin currently holds the following Non Executive roles; Non Executive and Chair of Audit at Financial Ombudsman’s Service, House Of Commons Commission, Corps Security, One Touch Switching Company.</p>\n\n<p>He also sits on the Civil service Pensions Board.</p>\n\n<p>He has previously served at Office of Legal Complaints, Office of the Public Guardian and Rural Payments Agency, UJ Atomic Energy Authority , CMA and the NHS.</p>\n\n<p>Shrin is the Chair of the Audit Committee for NWS and has particular interests in large transformation programmes, Risk Management, Finance and Developing Technology.</p>\n" .
